---
import JavaScript from "../../tags/JavaScript.astro";
import TypeScript from "../../tags/TypeScript.astro";
---

<section
  id="experience"
  class="w-full h-auto mx-auto container px-10 flex flex-col justify-between gap-8 max-lg:container max-lg:mx-auto max-lg:px-5 max-md:container max-md:mx-auto max-md:px-2 max-md:py-0 max-md:gap-4"
>
  <h2 class="text-5xl px-10 font-bold text-[#96F] max-sm:px-2">Experiencia</h2>
  <div
    class="w-full flex justify-between gap-4 px-10 max-lg:flex-col max-lg:gap-0 max-sm:px-2"
  >
    <article
      class="w-full flex gap-2 cursor-pointer px-3 pt-4 pb-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#08152C] dark:hover:bg-opacity-40 max-lg:pb-1"
    >
      <section class="w-auto flex flex-col gap-1 justify-center items-center">
        <div
          class="w-10 h-14 flex justify-center items-center bg-[#113B73] rounded-full max-md:h-12"
        >
          <span>
            <svg
              class="opacity-70"
              width="18"
              height="18"
              viewBox="0 0 18 20"
              fill="none"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
              <path
                d="M13 1V5M5 1V5M1 9H17M1 5C1 4.46957 1.21071 3.96086 1.58579 3.58579C1.96086 3.21071 2.46957 3 3 3H15C15.5304 3 16.0391 3.21071 16.4142 3.58579C16.7893 3.96086 17 4.46957 17 5V17C17 17.5304 16.7893 18.0391 16.4142 18.4142C16.0391 18.7893 15.5304 19 15 19H3C2.46957 19 1.96086 18.7893 1.58579 18.4142C1.21071 18.0391 1 17.5304 1 17V5ZM5 13H7V15H5V13Z"
                stroke="#F5F9FF"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="w-10 h-full flex justify-center pr-2 pl-4">
          <div class="w-[2px] h-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section
        class="w-full flex flex-col gap-2 text-[#F5F9FF] justify-between items-center max-sm:flex-col max-sm:gap-2 max-sm:justify-start"
      >
        <div
          class="w-full flex justify-between gap-2 max-sm:flex-col max-sm:w-full max-sm:justify-start"
        >
          <div
            class="w-full flex flex-col gap-1 max-sm:justify-start max-sm:items-start"
          >
            <div
              class="flex gap-1 max-sm:w-full max-sm:flex max-sm:justify-between max-sm:gap-0"
            >
              <h4 class="font-bold text-base max-sm:p-0">
                Desarrollador FrontEnd
              </h4>
              <span
                class="font-normal text-xs p-1 rounded bg-[#113B73] text-center flex items-center justify-center"
              >
                Actual
              </span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Comenzó en febrero de 2023</p>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-base max-sm:w-full max-sm:opacity-70">
            Zoftinium
          </p>
        </div>
        <section class="py-2 max-sm:py-1">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
            Crear nuevas funcionalidades, pantallas y comportamientos, basados
            ​​en la diseño predefinido para cada proyecto. Desarrollar los
            componentes solicitados dentro de los entornos establecidos,
            asegurando la uso previsto de la solución.
          </p>
          <section class="py-2 flex gap-2">
            <TypeScript />
            <JavaScript />
          </section>
        </section>
      </section>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  p {
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
</style>
